  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Logistics Coordinator",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Coordinate daily logistics operations including delivery scheduling and route planning</p></li><li><p>Arrange and monitor drivers’ schedules and attendance</p></li><li><p>Ensure timely delivery of goods to customers and internal departments</p></li><li><p>Coordinate warehouse loading and unloading operations</p></li><li><p>Handle external warehouse arrangements, including stock monitoring and rental follow-up</p></li><li><p>Maintain accurate inventory and delivery records</p></li><li><p>Liaise with freight forwarders, cargo agents, and transport providers</p></li><li><p>Prepare and follow up on cargo shipments and delivery status</p></li><li><p>Support customs clearance documentation and procedures</p></li><li><p>Resolve logistics, delivery, or stock-related issues promptly</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Job Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Experience in logistics / warehouse coordination preferred</p></li><li><p><strong>Knowledge of cargo handling and customs clearance procedures</strong></p></li><li><p>Good communication and organizational skills</p></li><li><p>Ability to multitask under time-sensitive conditions</p></li><li><p>Basic computer skills for record-keeping</p></li><li><p>Responsible and problem-solving mindset</p></li></ul>",
